  schema:description "A praxonic construct for tabletop and worldbuilding use: Hevî Mala, the recursive emission of care under collapse — a narrative lens, structural prompt, pressure diagnostic, and generative rhythm for stories where systems function without resolution and what persists is the rhythm of response." ;
